data.description:
Welcome to a breathtaking real estate opportunity that encompasses a sprawling 110 acres of natural beauty. Nestled within this vast expanse of land is a charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home, where comfort meets tranquility. The allure of wood flooring leads you inside, where all-electric appliances await in the spacious kitchen, offering modern convenience at your fingertips.

The master bathroom is a true masterpiece, boasting a beautiful standing shower and dual sinks that elevate your daily routine. The guest bathroom features a relaxing bathtub, ideal for unwinding after a long day. Picture yourself unwinding on the big front porch, basking in the serene ambiance that surrounds you.

Nature enthusiasts will be captivated by the beauty of the rolling land that extends into the Potato Hills, offering a mesmerizing backdrop to your daily life. The land teems with wildlife, from majestic deer to bears and turkey, making it a haven for nature lovers and hunters alike.

Discover the serenity of two tranquil ponds, inviting you to relax and connect with nature. Just 25 minutes away, Sardis Lake beckons with its water-based activities and soothing landscapes, while the vibrant town of Talihina, OK, offers both convenience and community.

Adding to the property's allure, an old house awaits transformation into a versatile workspace, providing endless possibilities for creative pursuits or practical projects.

Embrace the opportunity to own this slice of paradise, where comfort, natural beauty, and the charm of the countryside converge. Contact us today to schedule a private tour and experience firsthand the unmatched potential and serenity that this exceptional property offers.
